2. Project Key Enhancements

Requirements:
- Allow MULTI-SELECT for Project Keys (not just single like SPTOC1)
- Persist selection behavior

UI Improvement:
- Replace heavy message:
  "No projects cached, click refresh project to load from iTrack"

With:
